{"tid":626920,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"關於暗瘡疤","createTime":"2018-04-12T13:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T13:55:02.000Z","uid":19089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13fb239b6e505845fda966b9af1e22ee91ac1170","tid":626920,"uid":19089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"其實我皮膚都算ok，唔係成面暗瘡嘅人<br />\n依加只係黎m或太熱氣先會爆痘<br />\n但以前初中青春期嗰陣爆左一粒勁大痘係鼻頭，嗰陣又手多想佢快啲消失去擠佢，依加個鼻有個暗瘡疤，全面嘅暗瘡疤就係得依個（額頭就有小小印同暗粒，影響都唔大）但個疤係正臉中間，有時有啲反光位影，同影相啲燈光照到就會見到個疤<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇啲暗瘡疤療程好似好多都係for全面都勁多疤嘅人（標嘅價錢都得一個，全面千幾一次（應該係）），但我好似淨係整一個疤又貴左啲咁，想問下你地有冇嘅建議比我？或者有咩療程推薦？"},{"pid":"d0e9c64fc6060a5204fb5d8bb6fe9372cc23f227","tid":626920,"uid":3226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3860608d49404ca9c65e6f5e2adb50d4c329391b","tid":626920,"uid":110973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e9c64fc6060a5204fb5d8bb6fe9372cc23f227","tid":626920,"uid":3226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"太約幾錢左右?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋係咪藥房有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ce8c95532f927721385fdd85b5b3aafc8ba670","tid":626920,"uid":3226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3860608d49404ca9c65e6f5e2adb50d4c329391b","tid":626920,"uid":110973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e9c64fc6060a5204fb5d8bb6fe9372cc23f227","tid":626920,"uid":3226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"太約幾錢左右?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋係咪藥房有得買<img 